=== Access === * About 5 minutes by car from {{ill|lt=Aratano Station (Tokushima)|Q4784417|qid=Q4784417|lt=Aratano Station|1=Aratano Station}} on the {{ill|lt=Mugi Line|Q860478|qid=Q860478|1=Mugi Line}} of {{ill|lt=JR Shikoku|Q496531|qid=Q496531|lt=JR|1=Shikoku Railway Company}}.
